{"tid":1385732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重開］前線手足唔該入一入黎 裝備上面有建議","createTime":"2019-07-30T06:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T07:03:42.000Z","uid":42108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eaaef708ad785a4e1cbce902046c4fea9c20828f","tid":1385732,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:59:52.000Z","msg":"唔係想鼓勵你地龜縮唔做嘢 小弟發夢都係企最前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過已經幾次死裏逃生覺得好多人都忽視左<br />\n比狗追咬嘅時候如果打唔贏要走應該點做<br />\n希望你地都可以討論一下諗下計仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暫時諗到嘅係<br />\n<br />\n我極度希望前排嘅人<br />\n<br />\n你地齊裝嘅時候都唔該每人帶一個腰包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係背囊<br />\n即係下低呢個<br />\n又係decathlon<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.decathlon.com.hk/zh/p/500-ml/_/R-p-151313?mc=8547746&amp;c=黑色\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.decathlon.com.hk%2Fzh%2Fp%2F500-ml%2F_%2FR-p-151313%3Fmc%3D8547746%26c%3D%E9%BB%91%E8%89%B2&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmIwKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=158c95d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.decathlon.com.hk/zh/p/500-ml/_/R-p-151313?mc=8547746&amp;c=黑色</a><br />\n<br />\n點解？ 因為背囊根本唔適合緊急情況要攞嘢<br />\n同埋前線手足要攞其他工具係身<br />\n用腰包先可以裝到其他必要物資用黎撤退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二樣嘢要講嘅就係入面應該裝乜嘢<br />\n我暫時諗到嘅就係<br />\n前線手足一唔係就用保鮮袋裝一包波子<br />\n或者用呢個<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z7x5GUu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz7x5GUu.png&h=b119a92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裝油或者蛋液<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家個問題就係當班狗衝上黎咬人而我地又唔夠打走緊嘅時候<br />\n欠缺一樣有效嘅方法減慢佢地逼進嘅速度<br />\n咁樣搞只會令到前線俾人當沙包咁咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好容易連累自己人<br />\n到依家為止，好多手足都仲係未有開始用呢堆工具<br />\n希望可以提多次大家<br />\n場夢未發完，我地要趁時間許可嘅時候準備充足d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0edee9284d9da427265bb8fa9a140fccd059734","tid":1385732,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:59:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c17f4b1b34a4d504d090da989502ed2a49c35d9e","tid":1385732,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:00:21.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪無用定急速沈底"},{"pid":"f7568fc2e43341a7c089eea54ce9271e4f0a43b6","tid":1385732,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:00:32.000Z","msg":"幫手睇下比下意見"},{"pid":"9d5f26a37397bee0deab1480cc896641e5f14225","tid":1385732,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:00:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0a308fc4cc7840e5bd8f7637e74b82b2338402b","tid":1385732,"uid":1392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:00:47.000Z","msg":"夢想做工程師或者汽車維修員既同學仔入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383220</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫手推"},{"pid":"b0ae5f5adeb75833eabca3e495f95d5fa611e359","tid":1385732,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:01:04.000Z","msg":"希望大家討論下，好快就下一次發夢"},{"pid":"fc9b9a4c3afddba2d1fd906debe046947f534ab7","tid":1385732,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0a308fc4cc7840e5bd8f7637e74b82b2338402b","tid":1385732,"uid":1392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:00:47.000Z","msg":"夢想做工程師或者汽車維修員既同學仔入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383220</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫手推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"Push ed"},{"pid":"ca66286c88565fc8c190dda4e7a17a3cd820a7c3","tid":1385732,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0a308fc4cc7840e5bd8f7637e74b82b2338402b","tid":1385732,"uid":1392,"